      "lastUpdate": 1701947496760,
      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/error.jpg\" />\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nStatic Interaction\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nConvey a negative response, provide feedback that the input was rejected.\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:2;\n\">Design Tips:</span> \nThe tail was shortened to prevent unwanted vibration.\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> Amplitude</span> \n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Gain</span>:  default\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> default for gritty amplitude modulation\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\"> Emphasis</span> \nAdded additional points to the middle peaks to convey dissonance in tone.\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Frequency</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Audio filter:</span> default\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Haptic Output:</span>   default\n",
