      "lastUpdate": 1701947488863,
      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/open.jpg\" />\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nStatic Interaction\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nConvey a positive confirmation, provide feedback that the input was successful.\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:2;\n\">Design Tips:</span>\nThe amplitude envelope rises sharply with emphasis points added to the peak of each onset.\n  - The tail for the second event was trimmed slightly to shorten the event time.\n- The continuous peak was shortened slightly to increase the feeling of the emphasis\n\n/newpage\n \n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> Amplitude</span> \n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Gain</span>:  default\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> default\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\"> Emphasis</span> \n- Added to each onset to highlight the input. This makes the interaction jump and feel more convincing\n- Whitespace is left between the tail and the leading edge of each event. This helps to create a distinct separation of events \n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Frequency</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Audio filter:</span> default\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Haptic Output:</span>   default\n",
