      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/concrete.png\" />\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nMultisensory Event\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nConvey the feeling of a hard surface\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:2;\n\">Design Tips:</span> \nPeaks are increased to emphasise the feeling of the feet hitting the ground\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> Amplitude</span> \n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Gain</span>:  default\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> reduced to 20bp/s for smooth amplitude modulation\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\"> Emphasis</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Sensitivity:</span> reduced to 0% for smooth modulation\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Envelope Reduction:</span>  default\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Frequency</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Audio filter:</span> default\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Haptic Output:</span>   default\n",
