      "lastUpdate": 1701947536824,
      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/grass.jpg\" />\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nMultisensory Event\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nConvey the feeling of a soft surface, adding some texture to the individual blades of grass\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:2;\n\">Design Tips:</span> \nIncreased amplitude of the tail to give the experience more body.\nThe ending is cut shorter than the audio to reduce unwanted vibration.\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> Amplitude</span> \n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Gain</span>:  default\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> reduced for smooth amplitude modulation\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\"> Emphasis</span> \nRemoved all emphasis to kept the experience smooth\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Frequency</span> \nThe frequency is kept low to create a soft feeling\nModulating the frequency curve helps to add some texture\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Audio filter:</span> increased to 730Hz\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Haptic Output:</span>   default\n",
