      "lastUpdate": 1701947557387,
      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/football.jpg\" />\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nStatic Interaction\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nFeeling the impact of hitting or being hit\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:2;\n\">Design Tips:</span> \n- Increased onset width for extra impact\n- Brought back the start transient from '0' aligning with the audio, \nthis allows a stronger impact feeling\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> \n/newpageAmplitude</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Gain:</span> default\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> reduced to 10bp/s to create a strong impact rather than modulation\n\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\"> Emphasis</span> \nAdded mid frequency emphasis point to the first onset to create a punch\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Frequency</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Audio filter:</span> default\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Haptic Output:</span>  default\n",
