      "lastUpdate": 1701947570553,
      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/punch02.jpg\" />\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nStatic Interaction\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nFeeling the impact of being hit or hitting\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Tips:</span> \nThe frequency response is flattened where the impact occurs, to reduce modulation and create more impact on the punch \n\n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> \nAmplitude</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> reduced to 15bp/s for smooth amplitude modulation\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Frequency</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Audio filter:</span> default\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Haptic Output:</span> default\n",
