      "lastUpdate": 1701947586333,
      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/banjo.jpg\" />\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nActive Objects\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nConvey the feeling of plucking a banjo string. It should feel staccato and sharp\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Tips:</span> \n- Breakpoints were reduced to shorten and simplify notes, space is created between each element to further define each string pluck.  \n- The tail length of notes and chords were reduced to tighten the experience\n- The timing for the missing elements was adjusted by ear and feel \n- Attention was paid to the underlying audio peaks to pinpoint the event timing\n- Tails of the chords were significantly reduced to emphasise the individual strings \n/newpage\n\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> \nAmplitude</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> reduced to 30 bp/s for smooth amplitude modulation\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Emphasis</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Sensitivity:</span> increased to 70% \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Envelope Reduction:</span>reduced to 0%\n\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Frequency</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Audio Filter:</span> increased to  860Hz\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Haptic Output:</span> default",
