      "lastUpdate": 1701947578672,
      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/guitar03.jpg\" />\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nActive Objects\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nConvey the feeling of plucking a guitar string and strumming a chord\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Tips:</span> \n- In this experience the haptic envelope is modified away from the audio envelope\n- Breakpoints were reduced to shorten and simplify notes, space is created between each element to further define each string pluck\n- The trail length of notes and chords are reduced to tighten the experience\n/newpage\n- The tail of the chord was reduced to prevent excessive vibration as the chord resonates and fades out\n- The ending contained a few unexpected transients in the audio analysis, these were removed from the ending chord and the missing elements were added manually\n\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> \nAmplitude</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> reduced to 35bp/s to shorten and simplify notes\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Emphasis</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Sensitivity:</span> increased to 80%, Emphasis points are removed in the final chord. The amplitude peaks were raised to allow the chord elements to come through\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Envelope Reduction:</span> reduced to 0% ",
