      "lastUpdate": 1701947594174,
      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/mallet.jpg\" />\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nActive Objects\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nConvey the feeling of a mallet striking wooden bars\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Tips:</span> \nThe Emphasis points are removed to convey the thud of the mallet, this will feel softer than a guitar string\n\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> \nAmplitude</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> reduced to 15 bp/s for smooth amplitude modulation and simplified transition between notes.\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Emphasis</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Sensitivity:</span> reduced to 0% \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Envelope Reduction:</span> reduced to 0%\n\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Frequency</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Audio Filter:</span> increased to  720Hz\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Haptic Output:</span> default",
