      "markers": [
        {
          "id": "1bfa9d32-154a-4e6a-bd46-bc04437ddcc6",
          "name": "Oar Rising",
          "time": 1.504646630232558,
          "isHighlighted": false,
          "isEditing": false,
          "isVisible": true
        }
      ],
      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/roaring.jpg\" />\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nMultisensory Event\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nConvey the feeling of the paddle entering the water and feeling the resistance as the paddle is underwater. When the oar is pulled out of the water the resistance should feel lighter.\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Tips:</span> \n- The timing of the oar rising in the water was pinpointed using the audio asset in a DAW, a reference marker was added into the Haptic Studio project\n- An extra design element was added to feel the water drops falling off the paddle into the water\n/newpage\n- Transients are added over the continuous signal to represent the water drops falling from the oar to the surace\n- The frequency of the emphasis points is high to allow the water droplet elements to come through\n- The tail is shortened to tidy the experience\n\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> \nAmplitude</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> reduced to 20 bp/s for smooth amplitude modulation.\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Emphasis</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Sensitivity:</span> reduced to 0%\nEmphasis points are added to simulate water drops hitting the surface of the water in a random pattern. \n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Frequency</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Audio Filter:</span> increased slightly to 630 Hz to lower the high frequency ceiling\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Haptic Output:</span> default\n",
