      "lastUpdate": 1701947599803,
      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/rain.jpg\" />\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nMultisensory Event\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nConvey the feeling of raindrops hitting a surface\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Tips:</span> \n- Emphasis points are used to simulate water drops hitting the surface in a random pattern \n- The frequency of the emphasis points is high to allow the elements to come through\n\n/newpage\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> \nAmplitude</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Gain:</span> increased to +5.9dB,\nthis helps with transient detection and increases the intensity of the haptics\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> increased to 50 bp/s to increase transient detection \n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Emphasis</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Sensitivity:</span>  increased to 100%\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Envelope Reduction:</span> default\n\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Frequency</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Audio Filter:</span> default \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Haptic Output:</span> default\n",
