      "lastUpdate": 1701947624245,
      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/boxopen.jpg\" />\n\n \n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nMultisensory Event\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nConvey the creak of the old box lid opening. A solid thud should be felt when closing the latch.\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Tips:</span> \n- The initial creak of the box lid was increased with an amplitude ramp\n- Emphasis point was added where the latch is closed to make the action feel more pronounced, the tail is also extended\n- Space was added before the emphasis point to allow the motor to rest for further impact\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> \nAmplitude</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Gain:</span> increased slightly to +1.1dB\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> default\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Emphasis</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Sensitivity</span>  default\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Envelope Reduction:</span> default\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Frequency</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Audio Filter:</span>   increased to 630Hz\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Haptic Output:</span> default\n",
