      "notes": "Whether you're new to haptic design or looking to refine your skills, this tutorial takes you through practical examples with design tips to enhance your expertise in haptic design. \n\nYou can explore various interaction categories, get insights into the design intent and explore creative analysis settings. Included are some tips to experiment with and explore in your own designs. \n\nIt’s an interactive guide where each example can be looked at individually.  Feel free to play around and feel the differences.\n\nEnjoy!\n",
