      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/carstart.jpg\" />\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nMultisensory Event\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nConvey the experience of sitting in a car and feeling the engine start and rumble\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Tips:</span> \n- Separated this event into 'start' and 'revving'\n- Increased the height and width of the first event when the engine starts and revs\n- Removed intermittent transients to smooth out the motor idle\n- Added more impact to second engine revving event\n\n/newpage\n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> \nAmplitude</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Gain:</span> default\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> reduced to 15 bp/s to accentuate amplitude modulation\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Frequency</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Audio Filter:</span>  decreased to 570 Hz to emphasise the low frequencies\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Haptic Output:</span> default\n",
