      "lastUpdate": 1701947639728,
      "notes": "<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/window.jpg\" />\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600; line-height:1.5;\n\">Category:</span> \nMultisensory Event\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Intent:</span> \nConvey the feeling of a window servo engaging - allowing the window to open and close\n\n<span style=\"color: #E4E6EB;\nfont-weight: 600;line-height:1.5;\n\">Design Tips:</span> \n- Take note of the servo switching on and off in the audio sample\n- Increased the amplitude of the first transient and continuous event to increase the impact\n- Added a transient to the window close\n- Created space between the last transient and continuous signal for more impact\n\n/newpage\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2\"> \nAmplitude</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Gain:</span> default\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Resolution:</span> reduced to 20 bp/s for smooth amplitude modulation. \n\n\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF99;\nmargin: 8px 0px 12px;\nfont-size: 11px;\nfont-weight: 400;\nline-height: 16px;\ntext-transform: uppercase; line-height:2;\">Frequency</span> \n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Audio Filter:</span>   increased to 780 Hz\n<span style=\"\nfont-weight: 600;\n\">Haptic Output:</span> default\n\n",
